{"he567dd35gff04g4e11g841fgb4d4720a8eeb": ["*The corpse does not stir. It will answer no more questions.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_DeadFisherman2_Dead.html", "59296d21-ff6e-c1e4-af87-ccbfc8015553"], "hf11014b3g802fg4dbeg9dabg4a367c8da86e": ["*The corpse regards you lifelessly.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_DeadFisherman2_Dead.html", "716228f2-902b-f4d8-ce07-9824336d7f2f"], "hf6d13c93g1374g4d2bga9d3g7729c7945284": ["Who are you?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_DeadFisherman2_Dead.html", "9af8d31f-ef62-8ff9-220c-af40b61b8d18"], "hcfdb25f1g77d6g4da0g928fg8f6d9c6e51a3": ["Marcus... Fisherman...", "abe4e897-f8d0-8ad9-22d2-1fd83f99091c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_DeadFisherman2_Dead.html", "6e917594-6d33-2c61-6c81-90d9f4ee1e92"], "h74dec1e8ge7adg4a01g9bd4gabab1961951d": ["What were you doing here?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_DeadFisherman2_Dead.html", "a76341df-a4a8-3a1f-f636-d9165c5abffc"], "h4647091age518g448dga7c9gb951af591785": ["Saw the crash...came quick...try 'n help folk...", "abe4e897-f8d0-8ad9-22d2-1fd83f99091c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_DeadFisherman2_Dead.html", "1b7b3f4c-28ed-9556-0320-474b5ba36008"], "hb67556cbg1a24g456fg9c0fg225fadf500d0": ["How did you die?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_DeadFisherman2_Dead.html", "c1c81693-d77c-4dd7-407e-b6faa08be0e9"], "h815d0c03g9000g4de3gbcd2g99c2857f382c": ["Brains...didn't see 'em comin'...", "abe4e897-f8d0-8ad9-22d2-1fd83f99091c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_DeadFisherman2_Dead.html", "d498ce96-bbde-e314-3c30-96e3d58f568a"], "h7eb477ffg1397g4f43gb570g1ab89508a74b": ["Why didn't you notice the brains?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_DeadFisherman2_Dead.html", "334a0e18-6687-68a4-4cb8-9065d4bdc363"], "h18bbe970g974bg43bag89aeg673707e5e518": ["Did anyone survive the crash?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83"